{"tid":2216016,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共開始進行「台灣關係普查」","createTime":"2020-09-24T11:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T11:20:32.000Z","uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1abf757c2286a1ddc6386ac2474a64001b8a4c89","tid":2216016,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:13:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">一紙公告揭露中國對台進行普查 陸委會：違反我方法令</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/09/24/3302239_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F09%2F24%2F3302239_1_1.jpg&h=4cb6fd9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民進黨立委王定宇在臉書分享一張中國社區公告指出，中共開始進行「台灣關係普查」，實情如何還有待進一步瞭解。（圖擷取自王定宇臉書）<br />\n<br />\n2020/09/24 18:13<br />\n〔記者鍾麗華／台北報導〕民進黨立委王定宇在臉書分享一張中國社區公告，他指出，根據網路提供的這張社區公告，似乎<span class=\"red\">中共開始進行「台灣關係普查」，中國過去一定也有進行在中國的台灣人資料蒐集，不過這次揭露的公告，看起來像是某種「普查」，實情如何還有待進一步瞭解。<br />\n</span><br />\n對此，陸委會副主委兼發言人邱垂正在例行記者會表示，我們會持續關切，了解相關意涵，如果有具體事證，顯示有在台相關團體或個人協助陸方向台灣人民不法索取個資，就有違反《個人資料保護法》情事，相關主管機關會依法查處。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3302239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3302239&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheA3kfWbBCvxMfTTNG0K1D1Y%3D&h=f34b2fba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3302239&h=9bc43f06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3302239</a>"},{"pid":"f9e85c215afd00d72252a674f7367423d3c4e8b1","tid":2216016,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b7770312250460f0e2807cd8fdb04e028a3e00","tid":2216016,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:14:55.000Z","msg":"普及人質計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan